{"tid":2390964,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺黃圈根本無得搞？","createTime":"2021-02-02T02:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T05:06:47.000Z","uid":126888,"like":19,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"93e65eda905d8030c148f40161dd7320e9eed777","tid":2390964,"uid":126888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"法國依家唔係聖人基本上做唔到黃絲經營唔到黃圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔出聲？藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     無通哂天話人知自己係黃？藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賺藍絲錢？ 藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     合作嘅人裏面有藍絲？藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前識過藍絲frd? 藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要一個唔小心，喺自己都唔知嘅情況下就會變成藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反要成為黃絲要經過千錘百煉，加入黃圈個政治審查仲嚴過做公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分分鐘仲難過入共產黨<br />\n成為藍絲好易，成為黃絲好難<br />\n喺呢個精英制下個個都「被藍絲」，然後過一排啲人又會喺連登問點解黃絲愈嚟愈少？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無哂黃店嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人去哂邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個革命未完做咩靜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲邊有黃絲，你地都推哂其他人做你嘅敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556eed8c7fd0bf7eae5c88b9327ed9100b27d5c8","tid":2390964,"uid":126888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"黃絲幫襯藍店 -&gt; 偽黃絲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲幫襯黃店 -&gt; 偽黃店！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor