49.000Z","msg":"鬥黃問題  文革式批鬥<br />\n<br />\n一直都有<br />\n亦一直有人提醒<br />\n今日都都仲係咁"},{"pid":"1b9819ea077a3afb05801ce857e0bf85e92e1607","tid":2390964,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:06:27.000Z","msg":"唱普通話歌都比人話藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c981e2025ab4408c4b87e2716949487e5b149a","tid":2390964,"uid":295459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"唔少研究指出<br />\n人類鐘意夜訓智商通常較高 主因係智力刻服人類要日落訓教嘅基因<br />\n<br />\n而而家呢大班完全順從於支那批鬥基因嘅人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係屌班廢柴又唔係 唔屌又睇撚唔過眼<br />\n<br />\n外國優質野唔學<br />\n睇下外國人鬥黃<br />\n想自己顯得特別黃 係由自己做起 要黃過其他人 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那基因就唔係<br />\n想自己顯得特別黃 係由他人落手 要其他人唔夠黃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得 藍圈呢種事都係好常見<br />\n例如CCTVB鐘回家5.1黃手套事件<br />\n<br />\n我明有時黃圈人數多<br />\n平均智商係唔會高過藍圈太多<br />\n但係學野要向外國好野學習是常識吧?"},{"pid":"61cf6c8798e2732407ca7c93853cb40adee44640","tid":2390964,"uid":131836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:10:58.000Z","msg":"拎cv出黎俾連登仔批核先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285162cd0f223bac27e6e4c0792677367f4ed719","tid":2390964,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"渣哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\"